<title>USA: Halter Marine Group Q2 share rises.</title>
<headline>Halter Marine Group Q2 share rises.</headline>
<dateline>GULFPORT, Miss. 1996-10-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>HALTER MARINE GROUP INC</p>
<p>	     Condensed Consolidated Income Statement</p>
<p>	     (in millions, except per share amounts)</p>
<p>				Six Months Ended   Three Months Ended</p>
<p>					  Sept. 30     Sept. 30</p>
<p>					 1996   1995     1996   1995</p>
<p> Revenue			   $180.4  125.9    $94.5   53.9</p>
<p> Income before income taxes    12.0   10.1	6.4    4.0</p>
