<p>Weighted average number</p>
<p>  of shares outstanding (a)    18.0   18.0     18.0   18.0</p>
<p>(a) Net income per share and weighted average shares outstanding for the comparable periods of the previous year are shown as pro forma amounts. The company made its initial public stock offering on September 26.</p>
<p>-- New York Newsdesk 212 859-1610</p>
